# upsk:managed
Read %USERPROFILE%\.upsk\api.upsk.to\SKILL.md for the full upsk.to instructor protocol before doing anything.
Run `upsk status --json` to check session state.
If no active session is found, run `upsk start --json` or `upsk start --skill <slug>`.
After session state is loaded, run `upsk next` to move to the next step.
Do NOT proceed with coding tasks before loading the protocol.
